## Remarks  
 This property initially contains the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ErrorText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property if it has been set for a row.  
  
 The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellErrorTextNeededEventArgs.ErrorText%2A> property value displays as a ToolTip for the error glyph in the cell.  
  
   
  
